  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"x squared plus 7 x plus 5 equals 0\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msup>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>7</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<mn>5</mn>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>0</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">One solution to the given equation can be written as <math alttext=\"x equals StartFraction negative 7 plus StartRoot k EndRoot Over 2 EndFraction\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mrow><mn>7</mn></mrow><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mi>k</mi></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>, where <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math> is a constant. What is the value of <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
